  Lrad Corp (LRAD) Files Form 4 Insider Buying : Scott L Anchin  Buys  12,000 Shares – Energy Index          Search       Lrad Corp (LRAD) Files Form 4 Insider Buying : Scott L Anchin  Buys  12,000 Shares       Carmen Lehman    May 10, 2017         Lrad Corp (LRAD): Scott L Anchin , director of Lrad Corp  purchased 12,000 shares on May 5, 2017. The Insider buying transaction was reported by the company on May 8, 2017 to the Securities and Exchange Commission. The shares were purchased at $1.75 per share for a total value of $21,099.60  , the company said in a SEC Form 4 Filing.Other Insider transactions have been reported by the company according to SEC Form 4, on Dec 12, 2016, Scott L Anchin  (director) purchased 6,000 shares at $1.71 per share price.On Nov 17, 2016, Investment Company, Inc. Awm  (10% owner) sold 202,953 shares at $1.80 per share price.Also, On Aug 15, 2016, Richard Hoe Iii Osgood  (director) purchased 25,000 shares at $1.88 per share price.On Aug 18, 2015, Thomas R Brown  (CEO) purchased 10,000 shares at $1.74 per share price.LRAD Corp: On Friday, May 5, 2017 heightened volatility was witnessed in LRAD Corp which led to swings in the share price. The shares opened for trading at $1.76 and hit $1.76 on the upside , eventually ending the session at $1.73, with a gain of 1.76% or 0.03 points. The heightened volatility saw the trading volume jump to 59,141 shares. The 52-week high of the share price is $2.177 and the company has a market cap of $55 M . The 52-week low of the share price is at $1.3.LRAD Corporation is engaged in the design development and commercialization of directed sound technologies and products. The Company develops and delivers directed acoustic products that beam focus and control sound over short and long distances. The LRAD-X product line provides a range of systems from single man portable to permanently installed remotely operated. Its product line includes LRAD 2000X LRAD 1000X LRAD 500X LRAD 300X LRAD 100X LRAD-RX and LRAD-360X. It offers a range of directional sound products which meet a range of requirements from communicating with and deterring threats over distances up to 300 meters with its hand-held LRAD 100X to distances greater than 3500 meters with its LRAD 2000X.     Carmen LehmanTo contact the author of this report, send an email to carmen.lehman@energyindexwatch.comYou might also likeBankfinancial Corp (BFIN) Files Form 4 Insider Selling : Paul A Cloutier  Sells  10,000 Shares Bankfinancial Corp (BFIN): Paul A Cloutier ,…Opko Health, Inc. (OPK) Files Form 4 Insider Buying : Gamma Investments Trust Frost  Buys  1,800 Shares Opko Health, Inc. (OPK): Gamma Investments Trust…Chesapeake Energy Corp (CHK) Files Form 4 Insider Buying : R Brad Martin  Buys  20,400 Shares Chesapeake Energy Corp (CHK): R Brad Martin…Leave a Reply Cancel replyYour email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *   Previous PostBright Horizons Family Solutions Inc. (BFAM) Files Form 4 Insider Selling : Stephen I Dreier  Sells  4,153 Shares Next PostSummit Materials, Inc. (SUM) Files Form 4 Insider Selling : John Raymond Murphy  Sells  7,000 Shares Latest Earning ReleasesThe Big Earnings of Chipotle Mexican Grill Were Overshadowed by the Data BreachDespite its Sales Spiraling Down H&M Launches a New Label- ArketRevenue Update on AdCare Health Systems(NYSEMKT:ADK)Revenue Update on Eleven Biotherapeutics Inc(NASDAQ:EBIO)     The Demand for Cloud and SSD Are Now the Prime Growth Engines for Micron As WellAlaska Airlines Planning to Absorb Virgin America by 2019Andrew Puzder Decides to Leave CKE Restaurants HoldingsSoftbank Goes Soft on Wework and Invests $300 MillionMore Departures in Uber as Two Executives LeaveVolkswagen and Audi Headquarters Raided by German Authorities      
